 It’s here! Season 2 of “Grow Up or Nuts” has officially premiered on YouTube and it’s packed with more fun, thrilling and exciting moments with your favourite girls. This season, all mysteries are solved and more truths revealed. In the first episode, Reki’s gurt feelings tell her she’s being watched and followed. This amazing series was shot by Setwerk Films, starring Sophie Alakija-Rammal, Efe Irele, Okawa Shaznay and many others. Produced by Efe Irele and directed by Jide “J Blaze” Oyegbile. Watch the new episode below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 